
  <sn><md>### Noun Clause{.text-center}

**Noun Clause** হলো এমন একটি Subordinate Clause যা Sentence-এ Noun-এর মতো কাজ করে।

অর্থাৎ, এটি Subject, Object বা Complement হিসেবে ব্যবহৃত হয়।

**উদাহরণ**

* I know **that he is honest.**
* **What he said** is true.
* The fact is **that he is honest.**

এখানে highlighted অংশগুলো Noun Clause।

Replace the whole clause by `something`.
* I know **that he is honest.** <br>
  I know something
* **What he said** is true.<br>
  Something is true
* The fact is **that he is honest.** <br>
   The fact is something.
</md></sn>
